# README: Optogenetic fMRI of STN DBS in PD Rats

## Title
Optogenetic functional magnetic resonance imaging reveals therapeutic feedforward circuits of the subthalamic nucleus deep brain stimulation in the hemi-parkinsonian rat

## Running Title
Optogenetic fMRI of STN DBS in PD rats

